1. Ja *primam* novac od svoje plate svakog meseca. (I receive money from my salary every month.)
2. Njegova majka će *primiti* nagradu za najboljeg profesora godine. (His mother will receive an award for best teacher of the year.)
3. Ako *primite* ovaj lek, bol će se smanjiti. (If you take this medicine, the pain will decrease.)
4. *Primio* je poziv od svog najboljeg prijatelja. (He received a call from his best friend.)
5. Ona je bila srećna kada je *primila* poklon od svog dečka. (She was happy when she received a gift from her boyfriend.)
6. Molim vas da *primate* ovu poruku ozbiljno. (Please take this message seriously.)
7. Oni će *primiti* nagrađivanje za svoj trud i rad. (They will receive recognition for their effort and work.)
8. Žena koja je *primila* transfuziju krvi mora biti pažljiva. (A woman who has received a blood transfusion must be careful.)
9. Da li *primaš* platu na račun ili u gotovini? (Do you receive your salary in your bank account or in cash?)
10. Kada *budem primio* informacije, javiću ti odmah. (As soon as I receive the information, I will let you know.)